projectsList.heading: Bamboo: A language learning application (Mobile / Web).
projectsList.summary:
My language learning app for custom language lessons | 2024.
This is written in Golang, React native, and optional OpenAI integration allowing the user to create custom language lessons in all languages, including personalised tracking and lesson creation.

projectsList.heading: XAI for fracture detection within X-ray images.
projectsList.summary:
Masters dissertation group project | 2021.
A multi-model NN in order to detect and locate fractures in X-rays, segments X-ray to determine location to produce user-friendly output (report and heatmap).

projectsList.heading: Secure & autonomous robot assistant for static and dynamic environments.
projectsList.summary:
Bachelors dissertation project | 2020.
An autonomous robot composed of face authentication, safe autonomous navigation and destination object detection. Collectively creating an end-to end functional assistant.
